<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">调整分配法，在遇到不能直接运用分配率的题目，但含有分配率的因数，可进行适当的调整，就可使用分配率进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">3465÷35=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 3465÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(3500-35)÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3500÷35-35÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100-1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=99</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>